metadata.name: Peace #1
metadata.description:
This is a collection of hand painted Peace symbols. 

Artist Statement: 
"While the world is at unrest. We are all going through these different world and life changing events together. 
There is still a pandemic, now a war, and all of us really just want is peace. This project is my attempt to spread a little bit of peace into the world." - JAY

The "Peace" is meant to be pushed fast and just done. Hence the concept of Pushin Peace. 

Every "Peace" is digitally hand painted and 1/1.

No two will ever be the same and each will be unique in its own way. 

Artist: JAY
Location Created: MANHATTAN, NEW YORK

March 13th 2022
